### âœ¨ PHASE 5.8 HIGHLIGHTS

| Feature | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| âœ… **Assembly Boosting** | Related memories boosted via activated assemblies |
| âœ… **Embedding Drift Awareness** | Uses `vector_index_updated_at` to ensure alignment freshness |
| âœ… **Repair-Resilient Retrieval** | Index is now **verified post-load**, with diagnostics and auto-repair paths |
| âœ… **Diagnostics Dashboard** | `/stats`, `/assemblies`, retry queue, and boost logs all surfaced |
| âœ… **Lifecycle Control** | Pruning, merging via background loop with config flags |
